Since last year I have started publishing fully open-source analytics on Dune Analytics related to DeFi projects operating on the OP Stack, particularly Optimism L2 and Base L2.
Given the difficulty in finding reliable data regarding DeFi usage, I offer the code open to anyone so that the community receives as much information as possible.

My dashboards provide the OP Stack community with data regarding:
- Velocimeter's DEX usage and data about BVM token on Base L2;
- Velocimeter Graphene's usage, a licensed fork of Carbon developed by the Bancor team, on Base L2;
- Poison Finance's usage, a fully decentralized and community-driven cross-chain RWA project, available on both Optimism and Base L2.

